scripts.name: Rewrite Microsoft Safe Links
scripts.description: Rewrites links starting with "https://*.safelinks.protection.outlook.com" to link to the website immediately. This feature comes from "Microsoft Defender for Office 365". Also disables any scanning for potential phishing sites, see also https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-365/security/office-365-security/safe-links-about?view=o365-worldwide
